Chapter 21: Complete User Journey Flows

Lovable must understand not only individual pages but also how users naturally navigate through the application. Ensure navigation paths between these steps are intuitive and frictionless.

21.1 Admin Journey

Login

Dashboard

Navigate to Customers (/admin/customers)

Open Customer 360 Workspace

Switch to Machines Tab

Select a Specific Machine

View Machine Digital Twin

View Currently Assigned Operators

Click Operator to open Operator Profile

View Assignment History

Return to Customer Workspace

Alternative Admin Journey (Approvals):

Dashboard

Navigate to Service Requests (/admin/service-requests)

Filter by 'Pending Admin Approval'

Open Request

Review Insurance Approval status and remarks

Approve Request

Receive Success Toast

Request Status automatically updates in the UI

21.2 Customer Journey

Login

Dashboard

Navigate to My Machines (/customer/machines)

Select a Machine

View Machine Details

View Current Operators

Click "Request Operator Replacement"

Select Old Operator (from currently assigned)

Select New Operator (from available pool)

Submit Request

Track Request Timeline

21.3 Insurance Journey

Login

Dashboard

Navigate to Pending Requests (/insurance/pending)

Open a Request

Review Replacement Details

Approve or Reject (with remarks)

Receive Status Update

Automatically load next Pending Request

21.4 Operator Journey

Login

Dashboard (Mobile-first view)

View Assigned Machine details

View Active Benefits

Check Notifications

Update Profile

